8. Cycle Sort :
Cycle Sort ek in-place comparison based sorting algorithm hai jo minimum number of swaps karta hai. Iska main goal writes (swap / assignment) ko kam se kam rakhna hota hai.
Har element ko direct uski correct position par bheja jata hai, aur ye process cycles me hota hai â€” isliye naam Cycle Sort.

Cycle sort Variant before learning atual cycle sort :
------------------------------------------------------
- agr element 0 to N ya 1 to N ki range me di ho then cycle sort kaise apply kr skte ho agr ye dono case meet nhi krta ho to nhi lag skta ye variant.
Note:- Cycle sort based on value-to-index mapping works naturally for ascending order only.
For descending order, we sort first and then reverse. in both 0 to N ya 1 to N range wale me.
