 Actual Cycle Sort :
--------------------
- agr array me 0 to N na dekr ke 0 to supppose 10 dede but wo sare numbers present na ho jaise ek array hai jisme 0 to 10 elements hai but , 6 nhi present hai 10 do bar hai, 5 nhi present
 hai, 7 nhi present hai? to kya ab isme mai cycle sort wo variant wala lga skta hu? not at all, yha pe hme jugad lgana pdega jo actual cycle sort hai
Basic Idea
- Har element ke liye ye check kiya jata hai ki sorted array me uski exact position kya hogi
- Agar element already sahi jagah par hai â†’ kuch nahi karna
- Agar nahi hai â†’ usko uski correct position par bhejo
- Wahan jo element mile, usko uski correct position par bhejo
- Ye tab tak chalta hai jab tak cycle complete na ho jaye
Example
Input: [3, 5, 2, 1, 4]
Output: [1, 2, 3, 4, 5]

âš™ï¸ Steps to Implement Cycle Sort
1ï¸âƒ£ Loop chalao i = 0 se n-2 tak
2ï¸âƒ£ Current element = arr[i]
3ï¸âƒ£ Us element ki correct position (pos) nikalo
  - pos = count of elements smaller than current element
      4ï¸âƒ£ Agar pos == i 
  - element already sahi jagah hai â†’ continue
      5ï¸âƒ£ Warna:
  - element ko pos par swap karo
      6ï¸âƒ£ Cycle continue karo: while (pos != i)  
  - naya element lo
  - uski correct position nikalo
  - swap karo
    7ï¸âƒ£ Jab pos == i ho jaye â†’ cycle complete



